snippet: Camilo Villegas made an eagle putt on the par-5 18th hole at the Honda Classic in Palm Beach Gardens, Fla., for a six-under 64 and a one-shot lead after the first round.
abstract: Camilo Villegas takes first-round lead at Honda Classic golf tournament.
lead_paragraph: Camilo Villegas made an eagle putt on the par-5 18th hole at the Honda Classic in Palm Beach Gardens, Fla., for a six-under 64 and a one-shot lead after the first round.

headline.seo: Camilo Villegas Eagles 18th for Honda Lead
